title: Confidence, Anxiety and a Scramble for Votes Two Days Before the Midterms
description: As candidates made their closing arguments on Sunday, Democrats braced for potential losses even in traditionally blue corners of the country while Republicans predicted a red wave.
dc:creator: Lisa Lerer, Jennifer Medina and Jonathan Weisman
media:credit: Hilary Swift for The New York Times
media:description: A crowd gathered on Saturday at a rally hosted by former President Donald J. Trump in Latrobe, Pa.
